聞第四權作用。<br />\n<br />\n香港攝影記者協會<br />\n香港記者協會<br />\n2019年6月30日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bq7xcwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbq7xcwj.jpg&h=94069b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iEnUqRo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiEnUqRo.png&h=2e641526&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc26256ec3099a62b11c84cfa353a650debc8ab0","tid":1268564,"uid":247903,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"真係唔知邊啲人先係畜牲了<br />\n知法犯法<br />\n非法集會<br />\n公然侮辱記者<br />\n呢班係中國人，咪撚認係香港人呀<br />\n岀到國，只認衰香港人！<br />\n<br />\n反港勢力！<br />\n擾民生，阻住人做生意！<br />\n係時候要以其人之身還其人之道！"},{"pid":"e5979281b7def06faa518ff4404577ae25ec3e70","tid":1268564,"uid":54957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:48:40.000Z","msg":"成班廢老傻閪"},{"pid":"8400fbae56ef9584a2f2601f8252cdb475219b0a","tid":1268564,"uid":11291,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:49:00.000Z","msg":"TVB記者後悔未"},{"pid":"cc743362c2341009c053a9b1a43e6d1f98373c03","tid":1268564,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a97cc8b3e76d9219058083ce8394117bb2fd38c8","tid":1268564,"uid":70418,"like":209,"dislike":0,"score":209,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:25:38.000Z","msg":"廢老唔知press係咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:49:25.000Z","msg":"要印殘體字"},{"pid":"aaa79bbf4f720573e177350411618192630ffcdf","tid":1268564,"uid":183567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc83e955afd572185c5a315a6a173ee6af4c1357","tid":1268564,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T10:23:14.000Z","msg":"今日下午在添馬公園的支持警察集會活動中，多名前線攝影記者受到集會人士辱罵、遮擋鏡頭、潑水、吐口水、扔泥土和恐嚇等方式滋擾，香港攝影記者協會嚴厲譴責事件，有關行為極具惡意而且針對記者，嚴重危害記者安全，損害新聞自由，削弱公眾知情權。<br />\n<br />\n立場新聞一名實習記者在立法會示威區被集會人士辱罵「做雞」，該記者已多次表明記者身份，集會人